messages.message:
<!here> reposting in slack, in case the email slips thru.

This is a follow up to the proposal I had sent out last week. We have a PR waiting to be merged for this change. We are using the “conservative middle ground approach” as mentioned in the proposal. The corresponding PR for this change is here: https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/11020

This is a change that touches a significant portion of our Python codebase (about 790 files). The PR has been approved and I plan to merge it around 10 am PDT tomorrow. If you have any concerns, please reach out to me before then.
